        "id": 2053788,
        "name": "Levi Pinsky",
        "username": "Levi_Pinsky",
        "avatar_template": "/letter_avatar_proxy/v4/letter/l/58956e/{size}.png",
        "created_at": "2016-11-11T18:18:15.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>Agreed - although my bottle took a long time to come around. I gave up on it after a few hours on Day 1 and basically accidentally let it sit open for two days on the counter, coming back to it out of curiosity.  Here\u2019s my note:</p>\n<p>\u201cSuper weird for the first two hours \u2013 a little musty and funky in a bad way. But it became glorious after hours many left open on the counter. By the end of Day 2 left open in the bottle, it was silky, fruity and lovely. Surprising turn of events.\u201d</p>",
