        "created_at": "2016-11-11T18:36:06.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>My bottle was not in any way funky or musty, though, i wondered if I should have decanted as it seemed to have some in reserve. So, your day 2 note is not surprising.<br>\nCheers, guys.</p>",
