        "avatar_template": "/user_avatar/www.wineberserkers.com/william_kelley/{size}/2314_2.png",
        "created_at": "2016-11-11T20:44:45.000Z",
        "cooked": "<p>I\u2019m just writing up my notes on the 2015 Bachelet-Monnot wines, including their Fussi\u00e8re; which, if I\u2019m correct, comes from the same plot which produced this wine (Bernard Bachelet was their grand-father and their father turned over some vines to them when the sons set up Bachelet-Monnot).</p>\n<p>The 15 is lovely, and the Clos de la Bouti\u00e8re bottling even a touch better. Very, very smart purchases in 2015.</p>",
